OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777486270
OL,3,CPolice investigate after elderly man
OL,4,Cand woman found dead
OL,6,FPolice are investigating the deaths of
OL,7,Fan elderly man and woman at a property
OL,8,Fin Doncaster.
OL,10,FOfficers from South Yorkshire Police
OL,11,Fwere called to Brockenhurst Road,
OL,12,FHatfield, on Sunday evening 26 April.
OL,14,FAn 82-year-old man and a 78-year-old
OL,15,Fwoman were found with serious injuries
OL,16,Fand were pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,18,FTheir family has been informed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
