OL,3,CPolice investigate after elderly man
OL,4,Cand woman found dead
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Ben Wood said: "Our
OL,7,Finvestigation is ongoing and we are
OL,8,Fworking hard to understand the
OL,9,Fcircumstances surrounding what
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,F"We are keeping an open mind, and will
OL,13,Fbe led by the evidence. However, at
OL,14,Fthis time we are not looking for
OL,15,Fanybody else in connection to these
OL,16,Fdeaths.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
