OL,3,CPolice investigate after elderly man
OL,4,Cand woman found dead
OL,6,F"We understand this incident will come
OL,7,Fas a shock to those in the local
OL,8,Fcommunity and beyond, and our thoughts
OL,9,Fare very much with the loved ones
OL,10,Faffected."
